<subSubSection id="56BD55419219EF009A75963FF65FD15D" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="941AD2E66753DB5756C1FB67AC0C21D5" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A59EAC39CB12B954CD98D14DD5B61BB9" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
New records: Zemen Gorge, Razhdavitsa vill. mouth of Shegava River, 09.08.2004, 4 w., leg. Y. Petrova; East Rhodopes, Kremen vill., 21.07.2009, 1 w., leg. ALG. Detailed occurrence data: 
<bibRefCitation id="8867142F6009C3B08BA17990E3819C49" author="Lapeva-Gjonova, A." journalOrPublisher="Biodiversity Data Journal" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" refId="B7741022" refString="Lapeva-Gjonova, A., Borowiec, L., 2022. New and little-known ant species (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) from Bulgaria. In: Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." title="New and little-known ant species (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) from Bulgaria" volumeTitle="Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." year="2022">Lapeva-Gjonova and Borowiec (2022)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="11791E98851D8803870A131C79A5F999" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" type="notes">
<paragraph id="B2036802C1EF69253662C0C4A1F0833A" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EA52E047E689D445EB199CD05ADC9AE3" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
This is a southern European species with a range extending to Anatolia. It was reported only from Strandzha Mountain in Bulgaria (
<bibRefCitation id="CFB2806B3DD96DC09D83BB50D6A5B82B" author="Lapeva-Gjonova, A." journalOrPublisher="North-Western Journal of Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" pagination="72 - 84" refId="B7725840" refString="Lapeva-Gjonova, A., Kiran, K., 2012. Ant fauna (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) of Strandzha Mountain (Istranca) and adjacent Black Sea coast. North-Western Journal of Zoology 8 (1): 72 - 84" title="Ant fauna (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) of Strandzha Mountain (Istranca) and adjacent Black Sea coast" volume="8" year="2012">Lapeva-Gjonova and Kiran 2012</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
